          .input-field.col.s12.md12.l6
            input#password.validate(type="password", name="password" ng-model="pass")
            label(for='password') Password

        .row
          button.btn.waves-effect.waves-light.col.s12.md4.l6(type='submit',name='action')
           |Ingresa!

        .row
